persons: Elizabeth II, Queen of Great Britain
subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Royal Family
lead_paragraph: In a return to royal traditions, Andy Murray and Jarkko Nieminen bowed to Queen Elizabeth II at Wimbledon, who visited the tournament for the first time since 1977.
